==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr}} {{term|vermeil||vermilion|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|vermiculus||little worm|lang=la}}, the coccus Indicus, from {{term|vermis||worm|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/vɜː(ɹ)ˈmɪl.jən/}}, {{SAMPA|/v3:(r)"mIl.j@n/}}
* {{rhymes|ɪljən}}

===Alternative forms===
* [[vermillion]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

